1. Šetamo se duž *obale* Save. (*obale* - "shore") (We are taking a walk along the banks of the Sava river.)
2. Naša kuća se nalazi na *obali* Dunava. (*obali* - "coast") (Our house is located on the coast of the Danube river.)
3. Zagađenje *obala* reke je postalo veliki ekološki problem. (*obala* - "riverbanks") (Pollution of the riverbanks has become a major environmental problem.)
4. Ljubitelji pecanja često posećuju *obale* jezera. (*obale* - "shores") (Fishing enthusiasts often visit the shores of the lake.)
5. U ovom delu grada su svi parkovi u blizini *obale* mora. (*obale* - "seashore") (In this part of the city, all parks are near the seashore.)
6. Kupanje je dozvoljeno samo na *obeleženim obalama* jezera. (*obeleženim obalama* - "marked shores") (Swimming is only allowed at the marked shores of the lake.)
7. Turisti su oduševljeni *peščanim obalama* naše zemlje. (*peščanim obalama* - "sandy coasts") (Tourists are thrilled with the sandy coasts of our country.)
8. Naše najlepše plaže su smeštene na *obalama* Jadranskog mora. (*obalama* - "coasts") (Our most beautiful beaches are located on the coasts of the Adriatic Sea.)